sentence: We have acted as counsel to Acorda Therapeutics, Inc., a Delaware corporation (the “ Company ”), in connection with the registration by the Company under the Securities Act of 1933, as amended (the “ Act ”), of 1,563,627 shares of the Company ’ s Common Stock, par value $ 0.001 per share (the “ Shares ”), issuable under the Company ’ s 2006 Employee Incentive Plan (as amended, the “ Plan ”), pursuant to the registration statement on Form S-8 filed with the Securities and Exchange Commission on June 8, 2011 (such registration statement is referred to herein as the “ Registration Statement ”).
